---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Publish articles

Usage: mf publish [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  run     Publish article to a target (supported: local, yuque-prompt)
  update  Update a publish_records entry in mind-index.yaml

Options:
      --root <PATH>      
      --config <PATH>    
  -v, --verbose...       
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
